    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The exterior paint still shines beautifully, though you will notice a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and some light surface scratches near the door handles upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery is in great shape, showing only slight wear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine. All scheduled maintenance is up to date, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It is a reliable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
