    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in superlative condition. Every surface reflects a commitment to preservation that satisfies the most rigorous standards of quality and performance. This is an investment-grade vehicle, offering an unrivaled ownership experience for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection.",
