    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this car to believe it. It's in absolutely stunning condition\u2014literally like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this beauty is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
