      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a museum-grade example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 masterpiece. Featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline, the powertrain delivers immediate throttle response and linear power delivery. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior mechanical grip. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with rod bearings and throttle actuators preemptively serviced to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis remains tight, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to bridge the gap between track-focused stiffness and daily compliance. Finished in pristine Alpine White with no subframe fatigue or fluid seepage, this collector-grade icon represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in mint condition. Flawless exterior. Interior like new. Low mileage. Clean title in hand.",
