    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless, mirror-like finish with no chips or scratches, while the interior remains pristine, showing no signs of wear on the premium leather surfaces or controls. Meticulously cared for, it has been stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. Every maintenance interval was performed early at a certified dealership, with a complete service history included. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time-capsule' example that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
